SubjectNational Inquiry into Missing and Murdered Indigenous Women and Girls- Final Report
PrecisOrder transmitting the FINAL REPORT of the COMMISSION in relation to the National Inquiry into Missing and Murdered Indigenous Women and Girls, entitled RECLAIMING POWER AND PLACE, which Commission was issued pursuant to Order in Council P.C. 2016-736 of August 2, 2016, as amended by Orders in Council P.C. 2018-686 of June 6, 2018 and P.C. 2019-321 of April 10, 2019.
